38429.name: Share of consumer expenditure on food (USDA (2017))
38429.description: Percentage of consumer expenditure on food.

source.name: Consumer expenditure on food - USDA (2017)
source.dataPublishedBy: United States Department of Agriculture (USDA) Economic Research Service
source.additionalInfo:
Data on the share of consumer expenditure spent on food, and on alcoholic beverages and tobacco are given as the percentage of total consumer expenditures per person.

Data on overall annual consumer expenditure, and that spend on food is given in US$ per year.
